{"tid":37463,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔明點解大學course evaluation要係考試前做","createTime":"2016-12-13T10:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T07:51:13.000Z","uid":35870,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf6d5992f879f8782e07785287e23cd4505c77c","tid":37463,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"你唔考試，又點知呢個course教到你幾多野呢？<br />\n<br />\n你唔真正上戰場，又點知你老師professor教你嘅野有無用呢？又點知佢教你教得好唔好呢？所以係呢個情形底下做嘅evaluation係不能夠justify<br />\n<br />\n好多時，你教緊我個陣明明明晒，但一入到去試場又唔識，特別係有時pastpaper,notes 見都未見過你又出係到，即係想點？咪即係同以前d撚樣師父一樣，教人永遠留一手，教你九成功力，留番一招到時可以KO你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，廢事教識徒弟無師父嘅道理係一撚樣 <br />\n咁姐係你教得唔夠好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你教得唔好，又無機會畀我evaluate你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49544170bdabc2dfda10da9549257420a65afb34","tid":37463,"uid":1137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:57:46.000Z","msg":"Agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班仆街就係考啲平時上堂無教既 到我考試就知收皮，但係又唔知點解一定會有人勁高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比啲nds屌打"},{"pid":"07525a1029c729e838a259a4795ccc2edce9c674","tid":37463,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班仆街就係考啲平時上堂無教既 到我考試就知收皮，但係又唔知點解一定會有人勁高分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比啲nds屌打</blockquote><br />\n有陣時，我畀左勁低分個prof,但完sem之後先有d後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，想畀番高分<br />\n<br />\n至於勁高分呢個問題，就必然嘅，假設呢個世界係跟住normal distribution 嘅方向玩，所以無論幾難，但一定有人高分<br />\n<br />\n但問題係，個distribution curve中間點，同成條curve嘅deviation,係更值得研究，反映份卷嘅難道同prof教得好唔好"},{"pid":"280105d3f1ad027f412f127ed5fda36ac409f1c3","tid":37463,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517cdfc6498879bc51a45db8f3fb460d6cd73d71","tid":37463,"uid":61999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"哲學撚"},{"pid":"5316bd53a0664ee0befc95133628fd9e3baa932a","tid":37463,"uid":2235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bde66e450d78fdff77084d4d49d26e56df5737","tid":37463,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T13:20:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bbbd62be05579d9c8f72f6eef37bebf758eb8f","tid":37463,"uid":40330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T06:31:23.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"5f2281f83d524a4d2590515405b9fdb5ecfd8f52","tid":37463,"uid":13294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"認真，因為理論上學習唔係為左考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">可能</span>唔想考試既內容影響學生對教學質量既判斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}